1.
User Story
    As a TSMC engineer, time is money, I want to take Uber to the company every weekday at the same time, without using Uber’s app to make the order.

Acceptance Criteria
	The system will automatically appoint a driver to the user’s house every day if the user has signed a contract with Uber.

2.
User Story
	As a common user, I want to check if the driver has already taken three vaccine doses.

Acceptance Criteria
	The system supplies a bottom to let drivers change the numbers of doses they have taken.
